&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(101, 94, 155);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Overview&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Avanath is proud to be named one of the top property management companies to provide affordable housing for the workforce.&lt;/p&gt;
