&lt;p&gt;In exercising their responsibilities, they must promote an atmosphere necessary to support the greatest possible satisfaction and well-being of all individuals associated with the properties, including fellow team members and residents, and consistent with the goals and objectives of the Company and property owners.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
